<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今天的突破性故事|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com是您最新的中国新闻报道和时事的在线来源</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 03 Mar 2025 15:16:37 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>随着周二截止日期的临近，特朗普决定在加拿大墨西哥的美国关税水平</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/trump-decide-us-tariff-levels-mexico-canada-tuesday-deadline-approaches-2025-03-03/</link><description>预计美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）将在周一决定周一早些时候在加拿大和墨西哥征收什么水平，这是关于边境安全的最后一刻谈判，并努力停止芬太尼阿片类药物的流入。</description><pubDate>Mon, 03 Mar 2025 15:07:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/trump-decide-us-tariff-levels-mexico-canada-tuesday-deadline-approaches-2025-03-03/</guid></item><item><title>BYD考虑在欧洲的第三植物，在接下来的两年中决定，汽车公司报告</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/byd-considers-third-plant-europe-decide-next-two-years-automobilwoche-reports-2025-03-03/</link><description>中国电动汽车巨头比安特（Byd）正在考虑在欧洲建造第三种工厂，并将在1-1/2到两年中决定是否这样做，其执行副总裁斯特拉·李（Stella Li）在周一对德国出版物Automobilwoche的采访时说。</description><pubDate>Mon, 03 Mar 2025 15:06:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/byd-considers-third-plant-europe-decide-next-two-years-automobilwoche-reports-2025-03-03/</guid></item><item><title>中国的吉利介绍了新的智能驾驶系统</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-geely-introduces-new-smart-driving-system-2025-03-03/</link><description>中国汽车制造商Geely周一宣布了一个智能驾驶系统，即新的G-Pilot，该系统将在Geely Auto，Galaxy，Lynk＆Co和Zeekr Brands的汽车下可用。</description><pubDate>Mon, 03 Mar 2025 13:36:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-geely-introduces-new-smart-driving-system-2025-03-03/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾仔细检查可疑的中国间谍</title><link>ht