pubDate>Mon, 03 Mar 2025 10:06:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/chinas-trade-dominance-south-america-tempers-trumps-influence-2025-03-03/</guid></item><item><title>克里姆林宫说，有人需要迫使Zelenskiy与特朗普发生冲突后实现和平</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/kremlin-says-someone-needs-force-zelenskiy-make-peace-after-clash-with-trump-2025-03-03/</link><description>克里姆林宫周一表示，有人必须迫使沃迪米尔·泽伦斯基（Volodymyr Zelenskiy）实现和平，乌克兰领导人与美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的公共冲突表明，找到结束战争的方法是多么困难。</description><pubDate>Mon, 03 Mar 2025 09:59:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/kremlin-says-someone-needs-force-zelenskiy-make-peace-after-clash-with-trump-2025-03-03/</guid></item><item><title>联合国权利负责人对特朗普领导下的美国政策的指导非常担心</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/un-rights-chief-deeply-worried-about-fundamental-shift-direction-us-under-trump-2025-03-03/</link><description>联合国权利负责人周一对美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）领导下的“方向转变”表示深切关注，警告说，分裂性的言论被用来欺骗和两极分化。</description><pubDate>Mon, 03 Mar 2025 09:18:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/un-rights-chief-deeply-worried-about-fundamental-shift-direction-us-under-trump-2025-03-03/</guid></item><item><title>部长说，新加坡欺诈案中使用的服务器可能包含NVIDIA芯片。</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/servers-used-singapore-fraud-case-may-contain-nvidia-chips-minister-says-2025-03-03/</link><description>政府部长周一说，新加坡上周宣布的欺诈案中使用的服务器是美国公司提供的，可能包含了NVIDIA的高级筹码。</description><pubDate>Mon, 03 Mar 2025 07:35:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/servers-used-singapore-fraud-case-may-contain-nvidia-chips-minister-says-2025-03-03/</guid></item><item><title>随着骗局中心的镇压扩大，泰国念头墙壁的墙壁</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/thailand-mulls-wall-cambodia-border-scam-centre-crackdown-widens-2025-03-03/</link><description>泰国政府周一表示，泰国正在研究与柬埔寨边界的一部分，以防止非法穿越。</description><pubDate>Mon, 03 Mar 2025 07:05:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/thailand-mulls-wall-cambodia-border-scam-centre-crackdown-widens-2025-03-03/</guid></item><item><title>早上出价：特朗普国旗加密储备，妈妈的资金</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2025-03-03/</link><description>看看韦恩·科尔（Wayne Cole）的欧洲和全球市场前一天。</description><pubDate>Mon, 03 Mar 2025 05:34:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2025-03-03/</guid></item><item><title>中国如何增加其疲软的消费</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/how-china-could-boost-its-weak-consumption-2025-03-03/</link><description>中国一再承诺使消费部门成为经济增长的更为杰出的驱动力，但尚未实施任何结构性政策变化以实现这一目标。</description><pubDate>Mon, 03 Mar 2025 04:04:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/how-china-could-boost-its-weak-consumption-2025-03-03/</guid></item><item><title>债务削减计划提高了新世界的发展，但分析师仍然谨慎</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/shares-new-world-development-jump-after-it-vows-raise-cashflow-cut-debt-2025-03-03/</link><description>在香港主要开发商表示将增加现金流和削减债务之后，新世界发展的股票和债券在周一集会，但分析师表示需要一个更具体的去杠杆化计划。</description><pubDate>Mon, 03 Mar 2025 01:40:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/shares-new-world-development-jump-after-it-vows-raise-cashflow-cut-debt-2025-03-03/</guid></item></channel></rss>